%
% A customized CV style derived from CleanCV by Gilad Turok:
% https://github.com/giladturok/CleanCV
%
% This version has been substantially modified and extended for
% academic and industry CV workflows, including configurable CV types,
% custom typography, font management, layout customization, contact
% formatting, and reusable CV commands.
